    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines two additional policies for the Partially Reliable Stream Control Transmission Protocol (PR-SCTP) extension.  These policies allow limitation of the number of retransmissions and prioritization of user messages for more efficient usage of the send buffer.
	 </t>
